# Example: x_pointer_increment
# Goal: demonstrate pointer arithmetic and indirect memory access via X.
# Effect: writes three consecutive u16 words at 0x0200: 10, 20, 30.
# Run:
#   python3 run_sc1.py examples/x_pointer_increment.sc1 --mem-u16 0x0200 --mem-u16 0x0202 --mem-u16 0x0204

# X = 0x0200
9 0 2

# ACC = 10; mem[X] = ACC; X += 2
1 10 0
11
18 2 0

# ACC = 20; mem[X] = ACC; X += 2
1 20 0
11
18 2 0

# ACC = 30; mem[X] = ACC; X += 2
1 30 0
11
18 2 0

15
